    "description": "本課程主要在建立學生對於真空技術的基礎認知與應用，內容包括真空定義與氣體特性之介紹，以及真空幫浦、真空計、真空零組件、真空系統等硬體裝置之工作原理與實務操作等。維護等等的介紹，除了基礎原理之外，本課程亦針對真空技術在半導體設備的應用，提供產業資訊與技術的概況。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.真空定義與應用<br>2.氣體動力論與電漿概念<br>3.氣流與真空度分類<br>4.平均自由路徑與實務應用<br>5.真空幫浦實務<br>6.真空壓力量測實務<br>7.真空系統、零組件與操作實務<br>8.漏氣與測漏實務<br>9.真空於半導體設備之應用<br>",
        "en": "1.Definition of vacuum and its applications<br>2.The gas kinetic theory<br>3.Gas flow and degree of vacuum <br>4.Mean free path and its practical applications<br>5.Vacuum pump and practice<br>6.Vacuum gauge and practice<br>7.Vacuum system, components and operation<br>8.Leakage and leakage detection practice<br>9.Application of vacuum for semiconductor equipment<br>"
    },
    "weeklySchedule": "WK1-3    Introduction to Vacuum<br>WK4-5    Vacuum Systems/Short Report<br>WK6-8    Vacuum Compnents<br>Wk 9     Midterm Report <br>WK10-14  Process Systems Based on Vacuum Technology/Short Report<br>WK15-17  Practices of Vacuum Systems<br>Wk 18    Final Report",
